    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入一个无情的狂野西部世界，这里暗藏着邪恶生物，每颗子弹都至关重要。在 <strong>Western Shadowlands</strong> 中，你将面对一波波怪物敌人，通过升级左轮手枪和增强火力来生存下去。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324530/extras/591f9aafc45c72aebb7d334a09f9ce15.poster.avif?t=1732355170\" width=514 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324530/extras/591f9aafc45c72aebb7d334a09f9ce15.webm?t=1732355170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324530/extras/591f9aafc45c72aebb7d334a09f9ce15.mp4?t=1732355170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着每一波的来临，您和怪物都将变得更加强大，迫使您不断调整战略，以应对日益增长的危险。释放毁灭性攻击，发现强大的新能力，看看你能坚持多久，这是一场不折不扣的生存挑战——唯一的规则就是活下来，否则就会被黑暗吞噬。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324530/extras/782cfa4b2b8de7ddd0ceba4234c7a1ad.avif?t=1732355170\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324530/extras_big/782cfa4b2b8de7ddd0ceba4234c7a1ad.avif?t=1732355170 width=800 height=440 /></span></p>",
